At the broader state and federal levels, Frederick County's interests are articulated by a consistent Republican delegation. [Timmy French](/Timmy_French) (R) represents the county in the [Virginia](/Virginia) Senate, while [Bill Wiley](/Bill_Wiley) (R) and [Delores Riley Oates](/Delores_Riley_Oates) (R) serve in the Virginia House of Delegates. In the distant halls of the U.S. House of Representatives, [Ben Cline](/Ben_Cline) (R) is the voice for this district.

